{"tid":1901562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上水警察宿舍遭投擲汽油彈縱火","createTime":"2020-02-28T01:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T01:20:27.000Z","uid":320299,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe513cf1fba345dd103755ab666cb90d27ab18b","tid":1901562,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T01:19:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】上水已婚警察宿舍凌晨被人投擲汽油彈縱火，無人受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n便衣警員在宿舍外圍檢走膠樽、麵包袋及報紙返警署調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場是上水保榮路五號已婚警察宿舍，凌晨二時許，有人從宿舍外圍投擲懷疑汽油彈，擊中車場一輛私家車。<br />\n<br />\n於本月十三日凌晨，宿舍同樣被人投擲汽油彈縱火，警方正調查兩宗縱火案，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=382295&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382295%26refer%3DShare&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0SrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=bd13d3fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382295%26refer%3DShare&h=bd205cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=382295&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足好波 <br />\nmon po狗震哂未？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9c2cde03e861e404ba8e674d3a363adbe2556429","tid":1901562,"uid":320299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"突發！上水狗宿遭高溫消毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901447</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">原來有post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"}]}